  "rationale": "WoodWave lacks a logo-wall and feature-grid, so the SaaS story is mapped onto editorial vocabulary. The hero is the sole inverse bookend and only accent carrier, with the sanctioned display-title-over-media. The gallery-mosaic run (ghost-word + bleed + marginal caption) reframes 'everything in one place' as one continuous collected view. The three value_props render as ONE interlock feature run (float-wrap + inset + stagger) rather than a boxed card grid, honoring no-cards-on-cream. Social proof becomes an asymmetric stat+quote split on cream (no logo wall \u2014 gap flagged). A centered conversion stack closes on panel with typographic slash/arrow links (no buttons). Surfaces alternate inverse\u2192primary\u2192panel\u2192primary\u2192panel; assets use only the two real files (hero-staircase.jpg, overlap-vase.jpg), other media left null for brand photography."
